---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Get Urgent Help" }}>
	<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
		<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">
				Get Urgent Help
			</h1>
			
			<div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
				<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-800 dark:text-red-200">
					<strong>If you are in immediate danger or having thoughts of harming yourself, please call emergency services right away.</strong>
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Emergency Services</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Emergency - Call 911</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">For immediate medical emergencies or if you're in danger</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">Call or text 988 - Available 24/7</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Crisis Text Lines</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Crisis Text Line</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">Text HOME to 741741</p>
						<p class="text-sm mt-1">Free, 24/7 support for those in crisis</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">The Trevor Project</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">1-866-488-7386</p>
						<p class="text-sm mt-1">Support for LGBTQ youth in crisis</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Mental Health Resources</h2>
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">National Alliance on Mental Illness (NAMI)</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">1-800-950-NAMI (6264)</p>
						<p class="text-sm mt-1">Information, resources, and support for mental health</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration (SAMHSA)</h3>
						<p class="text-sm">1-800-662-HELP (4357)</p>
						<p class="text-sm mt-1">Treatment referral and information service</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">When to Seek Help</h2>
				<div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-lg p-6">
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li>If you're having thoughts of suicide or self-harm</li>
						<li>If you're experiencing severe anxiety or panic attacks</li>
						<li>If you're unable to function in daily life</li>
						<li>If you're feeling overwhelmed and don't know where to turn</li>
						<li>If you're concerned about someone else's mental health</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg">
					<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-green-800 dark:text-green-200">Remember:</h3>
					<p class="text-sm">
						You are not alone. Mental health crises are treatable, and there are people who want to help you. Reaching out is a sign of strength, not weakness. Your life matters, and there is hope for recovery.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
